recommend check-in -- Quin is seated and the elders retired cleanly, references repointed, the recent round swept. This changes the workspace's own voice identity, so it deserves Keaton's read before it settles fully; the one open judgment worth a word is whether any other always-on prose surface (foundations front matter, module READMEs) should also carry the Quin attribution, or whether naming it in the canonical style guide and rules is enough.
